column4: Hey all, trying to upgrade 10.10 64bit to 11.04, I get "E:Error, pkgProblemResolver::Resolve generated breaks, this may be caused by held packages." after waiting a while during "setting new software channels" step of upgrader
so what packages are being held
jetole did you md5 your packages, any of them just crashing out? what happens if you install a few at a time
I check, I don't think there's any
Any idea what else I should check?
